high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to the small box by the blue chair in the corner
Pick up the box from the floor
Turn right and walk to the front of the blue chair in the corner
Put the box down on the blue chair
Turn around and walk to the front of the TV stand
Pick up the credit card from the TV stand
Turn left and walk back to the blue chair in the corner
Put the credit card in the box on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card in the box on the blue chair

high_descs: Turn right and go to the chair in the corner.
Pick up the box from the floor next to the chair.
Turn around and walk in front of the chair.
Put the box on the chair.
Turn around and go to the TV stand.
Pick up the credit card in front of the TV.
Return to the chair.
Put the credit card in the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a credit card in a box onto the chair.

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the blue chair at the end of the room on the right, approach the left side of it
grab the box off of the floor to the left of the chair
move to face the front of the chair
place the box down on chair
turn around and walk over to the TV on the left side of the room
grab the credit card off of cabinet the TV is sitting on
turn left and walk back over to the blue chair in the right corner of the room
place the credit card inside of the box on the chair
anns.task_desc: place a box down on the blue chair in the corner of the room with a credit card in it

high_descs: Turn right until you get to the end of the sofa and then turn to face the box on the floor
Pick up the cardboard box off of the floor
Maneuver to your right so you are facing the dark blue chair
Drop the box on to the blue chair
Turn around and then face the TV on your left
Pick up the credit card off of the TV shelves
Turn back to the chair on your left
Place the credit card in the empty box and then close it
anns.task_desc: Put a credit card in a cardboard box box on a chair

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk across the room then turn to the right to face an empty box on the floor.
Pick up the empty box on the floor.
Walk around the chair to face the front of it.
Place the empty box on the Chair.
Turn around, walk forward 2 steps, then turn left and face the tv stand.
Pick up the card off of the tv stand.
Turn to the left and walk forward to face the chair with an empty box on it.
Place the card in the empty box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: To put a card in an empty box as well as place the box on the chair.
